Introducing an enhanced feature for "Scheduled Jobs" to help you monitor Apex Scheduled Jobs more efficiently. With this enhancement, you can now:

1) Monitor Apex Scheduled Jobs in real-time by tracking the percentage of scheduled jobs used.

2) Schedule Apex jobs directly from the All Scheduled Jobs page.

3) Manage jobs scheduled using a cron expression.
